Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.70,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由澄空学园制作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽·史尔特·穆斯贝尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便不直接触碰也能让人或者物品燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个善于生成火焰的「D」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  选择了作为龙的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急警报  紧急警报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒等级A  类型  青龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒等级A  类型  青龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永青之赫卡同克瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是  龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.55,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,40)\pos(578,72)\blur3}红翼龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.55,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,40)\pos(578,72)\bord0\shad1.5}红翼龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防御系统没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有注意到那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了就只好这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是  这么棘手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非战斗人员的诸位  请冷静下来  到宿舍的避难所避难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生了什么都请不要靠近学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在确认龙纹发生变色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此赫卡同克瑞的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是缇娅·莱特宁格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  筱宫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在没有被米德加尔的防御系统发现的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  现在只知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆出那么可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让缇娅感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次见到真正的龙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  拜托你担任缇娅的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物部悠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥有别的工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我想拜托丽莎你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被缇娅信任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并能够在情况紧急之时随机应变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有丽莎你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  你要走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么看  都是个顽强的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉尔和莲请到教学楼的屋顶待机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深月  我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝请和我们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾列拉请飞到空中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现有什么异变立刻向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看了  快点到避难所去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑龙的行动是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们连它们为什么环绕地球游走都还没弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  不要想着去打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡同克瑞是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算受伤也能恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一齐攻击也会这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前  尼福尔有过用燃料气化炸弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将全身同时消灭的成功案例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙现在已经完全复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所能做的是贯彻防御
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将受害控制在最小限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过例外情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份交易  我接受了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接  认可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你把我带到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是是想用和三年前一样的方式击退它对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只有哥哥你的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有能将赫卡同克瑞一时击退的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最后的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做跟那时候同样的事情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米德加尔也会受到巨大的损害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你用那种力量不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且  现在不用更待何时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要保护学校和缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要集中精神在这两点上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  有我陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会把你交给龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你孤独一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠他们  能赢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待丈夫胜利归来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是妻子的责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓「贤妻」就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把那孩子交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么傻话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs18}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒之枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么把戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会把缇娅交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的…是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  这些只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不懂事的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过  只要你老老实实把缇娅交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会好好地打赏你一番的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此我郑重拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  不行！快逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅  为丈夫看好家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是做妻子的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿吧  闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才有听到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的信奉者团体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始准备夺回缇娅·莱特宁格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米德加尔的防护很牢固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要入侵并没有这么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  那家伙就一定会出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  丽莎  丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我们要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会…让你带走她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经…约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让…你孤独一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…别太烦人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽·史尔特·穆斯贝尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎没有自我介绍的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也十分了解你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部悠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上唯一一个男性的「D」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领导龙信奉者团体的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认定为灾害的「D」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛  摆着这么可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想和你搞好关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞突然袭击什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是把物质变换成高热量物体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是想把这孩子带到巴西利斯克的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她到本应前往的地方去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总有人跳出来妨碍我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是你  还是那位小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对丽莎干了些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你没有老老实实地跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姑娘才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是缇娅不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  他也会为你而牺牲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不必为其而感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都不是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽  停手  不要做任何把戏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是实弹不行的话就用架空武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来杀我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我  我就停手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Nitro  bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氮气弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她进行了物质转换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,323)\fs18}Dark  matter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是能够看见上级元素才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为龙的新娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  做得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  将所有的虚伪抛去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做回真正的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是  谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅是  龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅已经作出了她的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们作出了约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才不是什么虚假的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是好好地存在于这里啊  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠人的男生可是会被讨厌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为巴西利斯克的配偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对任何人  对你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是最为幸福的选择哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我会陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会把你交给龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你孤单一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里才会幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅要留在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  缇娅要成为悠的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅是人类的女孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就让你无法作为人类生活下去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是利维坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是赢不了巴西利斯克的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会保护好缇娅的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都将回归于尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论谁都无法存活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对没有在今天把缇娅交给我们这件事而后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我让赫卡同克瑞先等了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过它似乎已经等得不耐烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡同克瑞可不会像我这般温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  做出决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅不是龙  而是人类的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想与悠  丽莎  深月  伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的大家一样活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要和大家一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永青之赫卡同克瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打不倒你  我就把你打飞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  枪皇无尽的法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Scarlet  innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无暇之绯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  打倒那条龙后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和缇娅结婚吧
